<sub>0</sub> and <italic>θ</italic>
<sub>1</sub> are the component density parameters. Following others [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR33">33</xref>], we assume that each mixing component is given by a zero-inflated negative binomial distribution (zinb), hence, for the <italic>j</italic>th component the density is
